      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>Correspondence of Kilpatrick and Pound, and articles by
         Pound as "Foreign correspondent" for the Richmond New Leader
         [17 items. holographs and typescripts signed] Other
         correspondents include: Ernest Hemmingway, Archibald McLeish
         and Harry M. Meacham [40 items. transcripts (mechanically
         reproduced)] Also, photographs of Pound &amp; Meachum,
         interviews, and newspaper clippings.</p>
      </scopecontent>
